14 Section 1273. As used in Section 1271 et seq. of this title:
15 (a) "Sign", "outdoor advertising" or "outdoor advertising
16 device" means any outdoor sign, display, device, notice, figure,
17 painting, drawing, message, placard, poster, billboard or other
18 thing which is designed, intended or used to advertise or inform,
19 but shall not include surface markers showing the location or route
20 of underground utility facilities or pipelines or public telephone
21 coin stations installed for emergency use.
22 (b) "Main traveled way" means the traveled way of a highway on
23 which through traffic is carried. In the case of a divided highway,
24 the traveled way of each of the separated roadways for traffic in
